WEBVTT

00:02.102 --> 00:02.868
<i>Previously on Medium:</i>

00:02.936 --> 00:06.071
I don't know how to do it.

00:06.139 --> 00:08.740
I don't know
how to fire these people.

00:08.775 --> 00:11.877
I want to buy back my company
and my idea from you.

00:11.911 --> 00:13.612
The business is not for sale.

00:13.746 --> 00:15.848
Your idea is not for sale.

00:15.882 --> 00:18.183
You are not for sale.

00:18.251 --> 00:20.119
(phone rings)

00:20.153 --> 00:22.154
If you're still interested...

00:22.222 --> 00:25.257
I'll sell you back your company.

00:25.291 --> 00:27.059
If you can get together
a couple

00:27.093 --> 00:30.295
of million dollars, we can
figure out how you can pay me

00:30.363 --> 00:31.530
the balance over time.

00:31.564 --> 00:33.132
I'm Cynthia Keener.

00:33.166 --> 00:35.667
I'm an investigator
with Ameritips.

00:35.702 --> 00:38.704
I guess she's hoping
I'll be able to help her
with some of her cases.

00:38.738 --> 00:40.305
<i>According to this,
Cynthia Keener</i>

00:40.373 --> 00:43.876
<i>had a daughter named Suzie
who went missing in 1998.</i>

00:43.943 --> 00:45.577
I had nothing to do
with her death.

00:45.678 --> 00:47.913
If you think this is over,
you're wrong.

00:47.947 --> 00:51.383
<i>Suzie... it was my job
to stand up for her.</i>

00:51.451 --> 00:53.619
<i>And now I finally have.</i>

00:53.653 --> 00:57.222
It's all right, Allison.

00:57.290 --> 01:00.159
I've called
the authorities.

01:00.226 --> 01:01.727
They'll be here
in a moment.

01:07.033 --> 01:10.769
(bird cawing)

01:17.210 --> 01:20.712
CYNTHIA:
You should have
that looked at.

01:20.747 --> 01:22.414
Could leave a nasty scar.

01:22.449 --> 01:23.582
(bag thuds on ground)

01:23.616 --> 01:24.917
MAN:
You're late.

01:24.951 --> 01:26.819
I was about to leave.

01:26.886 --> 01:28.487
Oh, I'm not sure I believe that.

01:28.521 --> 01:30.456
I think you'd have waited
as long as you had to.

01:36.396 --> 01:39.097
It's all there. Unmarked bills,
just like you asked.

01:39.165 --> 01:40.899
No tricks.
No transmitters.

01:43.303 --> 01:45.637
Where's Bethany?

01:45.672 --> 01:47.906
Down there.

01:47.974 --> 01:49.942
(bird caws)

01:49.976 --> 01:52.978
Oh, my God.
What have you done?

01:53.012 --> 01:54.646
I buried her down there
an hour ago.

01:54.681 --> 01:56.148
Figure she has maybe...

01:56.182 --> 01:59.785
five or six minutes
of air left.

