Bethany! Can you hear me?

02:15.435 --> 02:16.435
(thumping)
Bethany!

02:16.469 --> 02:18.403
Bethany, I'm coming!

02:18.438 --> 02:20.372
(panting)

02:20.406 --> 02:22.007
Bethany!

02:22.075 --> 02:23.742
Can you hear me?!

02:23.777 --> 02:26.879
Can you hear me?
I'm coming!

02:26.946 --> 02:29.281
Bethany! Can you hear me?

02:29.315 --> 02:31.049
(gasps)

